In-class Exercise 7

Author

Lim Jia Jia

Published

March 8, 2024

Modified

March 9, 2024

pacman::p_load(sf, terra, gstat, viridis, tidyverse, tmap)
rfstations <- read_csv("data/aspatial/RainfallStation.csv")
rfdata <- read_csv("data/aspatial/DAILYDATA_202402.csv") %>%
  select(c(1,5)) %>%
  group_by(Station)%>%
  summarise(MONTHSUM = sum(`Daily Rainfall Total (mm)`)) %>%
  ungroup()
rfdata <- rfdata %>%
  left_join(rfstations)
rfdata_sf <- st_as_sf(rfdata, 
                      coords = c("Longitude",
                                 "Latitude"),
                      crs =4326) %>%
  st_transform(crs=4314)
mpsz2019 <- st_read(dsn = "data/geospatial",
                layer = "MPSZ-2019") %>%
  st_transform(crs=4314)
Reading layer `MPSZ-2019' from data source 
  `C:\ljjiaa\ISSS608\In-class_Ex\In-class_Ex7\data\geospatial' 
  using driver `ESRI Shapefile'
Simple feature collection with 332 features and 6 fields
Geometry type: MULTIPOLYGON
Dimension:     XY
Bounding box:  xmin: 103.6057 ymin: 1.158699 xmax: 104.0885 ymax: 1.470775
Geodetic CRS:  WGS 84
tmap_options(check.and.fix=TRUE)
tmap_mode("view")
tm_shape(mpsz2019)+
  tm_borders()+
tm_shape(rfdata_sf)+
  tm_dots(col='MONTHSUM')
tmap_mode("plot")                                                                      
grid <- terra::rast(mpsz2019,
                    nrows = 690,
                    ncols =1075)

xy <- terra::xyFromCell(grid, 1:ncell(grid))
